snippet: Less than 24 hours after New England's season ended prematurely with a heartbreaking 20-18 loss to the Denver Broncos, Patriots coach Bill Belichick said his team were ready to turn the page and move on....
lead_paragraph: Less than 24 hours after New England's season ended prematurely with a heartbreaking 20-18 loss to the Denver Broncos, Patriots coach Bill Belichick said his team were ready to turn the page and move on.

headline.main: Patriots Will 'Turn the Page, and Move on,' Says Belichick
headline.print_headline: Patriots Will 'Turn the Page, and Move on,' Says Belichick
